OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will
OL,6,Fremain dry overnight with patchy cloud
OL,7,Faround at times, lowest over the
OL,8,FPennines. Isolated mist of fog patches
OL,9,Fmay develop in prone locations through
OL,10,Fthe early hours. Light to moderate
OL,11,Fnorthwesterly winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA day of variable cloud and
OL,14,Fsome bright or sunny spells once any
OL,15,Fearly morning mist or fog clears.
OL,16,FFeeling warm in the light to moderate
OL,17,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
