OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FConditions will turn cooler over the
OL,7,Fweekend with some wet and breezy
OL,8,Fweather moving through from the
OL,9,Fnorthwest, mainly on Saturday.
OL,10,FVariable on Monday with a few showers.
